<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.3.9">
<l>pulaṉkaḷ naiyamey yilmūt tuppōn tiruntuḷ ḷameḷki</l>
<l>kalaṅka vaikkaḷ pōta vuntik kaṇṭa pitaṟṟāmuṉ</l>
<l>alaṅka lāya taṇṭu ḻāykoṇ ṭāyi ranāmañcolli</l>
<l>valaṅkoḷ toṇṭarp pāṭi yāṭum vatari vaṇaṅkutumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Before I babble randomly, profusely hacking up phlegm,</l>
<l>The senses in [my] body having gotten age-worn so they weaken,</l>
<l rend="indent">as [my] heart flutters, faltering,</l>
<l>We will worship at Badarī where devotees who circumambulate [there]</l>
<l rend="indent">sing and dance,</l>
<l>Bringing cool tulasī as garlands, saying [his] one-thousand names.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
